# Scripts

| Script | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `release.py` | Build dist, validate, run audits (run before release) |
| `merge_plant_data.py` | Build dist/ from source |
| `validate_json.py` | Schema and structure validation |
| `audit_scientific_names.py` | Check commonExamples for accepted names |
| `audit_duplicates.py` | Genus/species overlap, similar typeNames |
| `reorganize_plants.py` | Apply REMOVE_IDS, CATEGORY_CHANGES |
| `improve_care_tips.py` | Apply category-specific care tips |
| `add_dormancy_notes.py` | Add dormancy notes for null winterInterval |

Edit `REMOVE_IDS` and `CATEGORY_CHANGES` in `reorganize_plants.py` before running it.
